OL,3,CCriminals with devices used in 40% of
OL,4,Ccar thefts face up to five years in
OL,5,Cprison
OL,7,FCriminals caught with electronic
OL,8,Fdevices used in 40% of car thefts face
OL,9,Fup to five years in prison under a new
OL,10,Flaw.
OL,12,FThe Crime and Policing Bill, to be
OL,13,Fintroduced to Parliament on Tuesday,
OL,14,Fwill ban the possession, sale and
OL,15,Fdistribution of gadgets such as signal
OL,16,Fjammers. The devices can be used to
OL,17,Fblock remote locks, allowing thieves
OL,18,Fto get in a vehicle without a key.
