OL,3,CCriminals with devices used in 40% of
OL,4,Ccar thefts face up to five years in
OL,5,Cprison
OL,7,FAnyone who is found in possession of
OL,8,Fone, or to have imported, made,
OL,9,Fadapted or distributed them, could be
OL,10,Fjailed for five years and receive an
OL,11,Funlimited fine.
OL,13,FCurrently, prosecutions are only
OL,14,Fpossible if there is evidence that the
OL,15,Fdevice was used to commit a crime.
OL,17,FHowever, police forces report that
OL,18,Fsuch devices are used in four out of
OL,19,Fevery ten vehicle thefts in England
OL,20,Fand Wales - rising to 60% of cases in
OL,21,FLondon.
