OL,3,CCriminals with devices used in 40% of
OL,4,Ccar thefts face up to five years in
OL,5,Cprison
OL,7,FPolicing minister Dame Diana Johnson
OL,8,Fsaid: "These thefts have a devastating
OL,9,Feffect on victims, who need their
OL,10,Fvehicles to go about their everyday
OL,11,Flives.
OL,13,F"We are aware of the real concerns
OL,14,Fpeople feel with the use of these
OL,15,Felectronic devices being so prolific."
